                <li>
                  <b>Keep Records</b>
                  <ul>
                    <li>
                      Maintain a detailed log of all maintenance activities,
                      including cleaning schedules, component inspections, and
                      any repairs performed. This record helps track the
                      machine’s condition and plan future maintenance.
